3db303","tid":1294493,"uid":3239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:49:18.000Z","msg":"邊個查?邊個告?<br />\n得律政司同執法部門可以全權處理犯罪,全部都係圍威喂<br />\n除非有其他方法, 民間可以自己組織人馬搜證, 訴訟, 告返警察<br />\n有我一定課撚爆"},{"pid":"18ec70f8526ef85f9e7425dd8d68bb3a36fec55f","tid":1294493,"uid":269566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf4a6e9a9649848708433dad07bc6f998c875a5f","tid":1294493,"uid":186744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:16:27.000Z","msg":"噚日有人做咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"結果係點？<br />\n有無人可以純學術上討論下"},{"pid":"1e89f431ed4012832477de3c1312c7b02e557dba","tid":1294493,"uid":24897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:49:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">!!請幫手廣傳!!<br />\n如見大量不名人士冇委任證<br />\n<br />\n如懷疑有人冒警/放走罪犯<br />\n<br />\n要即場錄低 打999報警(記著拎報案編號)<br />\n做個良好市民,打擊懷疑罪犯<br />\n點報案可向雲海學習</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1290992/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1290992/page/1</a>"}]}